des:
Health talk and Stories - Chandrima bolchi podcast will publish Stories in bengali and english for stress management. Stress – a twentieth century syndrome has a big impact on our health conditions. It is felt-by just us, and in ways the world can see.
In Health Talk, eminent doctors and medical professionals will give theirs frank opinions on health awareness, conditions, issues, diseases and its probable cures. 
The shared informations in this skill is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. 
Call your doctor for any medical advice. For medical emergency please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
